To Enable Camera:

sudo raspi-config

Go to: Interfacing Options -> Camera -> Enable

sudo reboot

take a test picture: raspistill -o test.jpg
take a test video: raspivid -o test.h262 5000


To Enable SSH:
sudo raspi-congig

Go to : Interface Options -> SSH -> Enable

sudo reboot

To connect via another computer:

Raspberry Pi IP: <here>
ssh pi@<IP ADDRESS>